1
00:00:17,160 --> 00:00:18,020
This is poison.

2
00:00:19,030 --> 00:00:20,230
I had someone test it.

3
00:00:21,230 --> 00:00:23,290
It won't take effect until tomorrow.

4
00:00:23,620 --> 00:00:24,890
It will be painless.

5
00:00:26,190 --> 00:00:27,550
To die tomorrow?

6
00:00:29,350 --> 00:00:30,320
What's the use

7
00:00:31,600 --> 00:00:32,750
of keeping me alive

8
00:00:34,280 --> 00:00:35,750
until tomorrow?

9
00:00:39,840 --> 00:00:42,170
Xiao Wuyi has agreed to cooperate with me.

10
00:00:42,670 --> 00:00:43,750
But now,

11
00:00:44,880 --> 00:00:46,740
there's still one thing missing—

12
00:00:47,000 --> 00:00:48,330
a pledge of allegiance.

13
00:00:52,840 --> 00:00:54,200
So you want to use my life

14
00:00:55,150 --> 00:00:57,080
to announce Xiao Wuyi's betrayal.

15
00:01:06,840 --> 00:01:07,480
Lejun!

16
00:01:08,590 --> 00:01:09,740
Have you lost your mind?

17
00:01:09,740 --> 00:01:10,760
This is a deadly poison!

18
00:01:10,760 --> 00:01:12,760
Wasn't it you who told me to drink it?

19
00:01:12,950 --> 00:01:13,590
But

20
00:01:14,310 --> 00:01:15,570
I could have found a way

21
00:01:15,870 --> 00:01:16,870
to keep you alive.

22
00:01:17,240 --> 00:01:18,700
Didn't it ever occur to you

23
00:01:19,070 --> 00:01:20,150
to beg me just once?

24
00:01:30,789 --> 00:01:32,320
But I no longer wish to live.

25
00:01:34,680 --> 00:01:35,509
Mulian Yu.

26
00:01:37,509 --> 00:01:40,680
What are you still pretending for?

27
00:01:42,000 --> 00:01:43,920
Did you bring poison here today

28
00:01:44,759 --> 00:01:46,400
just to hear me beg for mercy?

29
00:01:48,509 --> 00:01:49,479
Three years.

30
00:01:50,840 --> 00:01:53,039
You've been by my side for 3 years.

31
00:01:53,560 --> 00:01:55,390
Three years of marriage between us—

32
00:01:55,390 --> 00:01:56,570
all my indulgence toward you,

33
00:01:56,570 --> 00:01:58,280
all the affection I showed you—

34
00:01:58,280 --> 00:02:01,480
did none of it earn
even a shred of your genuine affection?

35
00:02:05,150 --> 00:02:06,040
No.

36
00:02:08,910 --> 00:02:10,440
Our homelands are enemies.

37
00:02:10,840 --> 00:02:12,190
All my blood relatives

38
00:02:12,190 --> 00:02:14,520
were killed by you Northern Qin people.

39
00:02:16,150 --> 00:02:18,680
Our families have been sworn enemies
for generations.

40
00:02:18,680 --> 00:02:21,610
How could there be any genuine affection
between us?

41
00:02:38,710 --> 00:02:39,680
Mulian Yu.

42
00:02:41,960 --> 00:02:44,310
Can you promise me one thing?

43
00:02:47,630 --> 00:02:50,280
If one day you win

44
00:02:51,030 --> 00:02:54,030
and lead your army to attack Jiankang,

45
00:02:55,710 --> 00:02:58,470
can you please

46
00:02:59,030 --> 00:03:00,430
spare my brother's life?

47
00:03:01,400 --> 00:03:03,120
He's the only family

48
00:03:03,680 --> 00:03:05,280
I have left in this world.

49
00:03:08,590 --> 00:03:09,320
Ridiculous.

50
00:03:11,080 --> 00:03:12,480
Absolutely ridiculous.

51
00:03:17,280 --> 00:03:18,590
If Heaven favors me

52
00:03:19,750 --> 00:03:21,150
and that day truly comes.

53
00:03:22,310 --> 00:03:24,040
I'll kill him with my own hands.

54
00:03:27,240 --> 00:03:29,500
That way, you two can be reunited sooner,

55
00:03:30,120 --> 00:03:33,470
and it won't have been in vain
that you submitted yourself to the enemy,

56
00:03:33,470 --> 00:03:35,980
exhausting your wits

57
00:03:37,000 --> 00:03:39,400
and plotting your entire life
for his sake.

58
00:03:43,560 --> 00:03:44,590
Mulian Yu!

59
00:03:50,630 --> 00:03:51,680
I'm sorry.

60
00:04:02,910 --> 00:04:04,080
Sorry that

61
00:04:05,590 --> 00:04:07,650
I've schemed against you once again.

62
00:04:08,590 --> 00:04:09,850
If there is a next life,

63
00:04:10,590 --> 00:04:13,150
may we meet again
with different identities.

64
00:06:18,620 --> 00:06:23,000
[Key to the Phoenix Heart]

65
00:06:23,080 --> 00:06:25,910
[Episode 27]

66
00:06:27,070 --> 00:06:28,390
Xiao Wuyi!

67
00:06:40,159 --> 00:06:41,830
If you truly have faith in him,

68
00:06:43,240 --> 00:06:44,480
please allow him

69
00:06:45,560 --> 00:06:48,680
to stand before you as a true rival.

70
00:07:25,800 --> 00:07:26,270
Lejun.

71
00:07:27,240 --> 00:07:27,720
Lejun!

72
00:07:29,670 --> 00:07:34,810
♪ The past is dust,
we're passing through ♪

73
00:07:33,159 --> 00:07:33,720
Lejun!

74
00:07:35,740 --> 00:07:41,320
♪ No regrets for what we've lost and won ♪

75
00:07:35,800 --> 00:07:36,310
Lejun.

76
00:07:37,070 --> 00:07:37,870
Mao.

77
00:07:38,120 --> 00:07:39,040
I came too late.

78
00:07:40,000 --> 00:07:43,920
You finally came to pick me up.

79
00:07:41,980 --> 00:07:48,280
♪ The shape of time begins to fade ♪

80
00:07:45,040 --> 00:07:45,560
Lejun.

81
00:07:48,390 --> 00:07:51,270
I... I want to go home.

82
00:07:48,550 --> 00:07:55,030
♪ Half by choice, half washed away ♪

83
00:07:52,270 --> 00:07:54,360
Lejun... Lejun...

84
00:07:55,540 --> 00:08:00,960
♪ If fate is fragile,
what is right or wrong? ♪

85
00:07:55,920 --> 00:07:56,430
Go...

86
00:08:01,560 --> 00:08:06,930
♪ We only live for what we can't let go ♪

87
00:08:07,730 --> 00:08:11,380
♪ Love and hate fade
like the shifting sand ♪

88
00:08:11,480 --> 00:08:13,930
♪ What's right or wrong is better
left unsaid ♪

89
00:08:12,950 --> 00:08:13,680
Lejun!

90
00:08:14,160 --> 00:08:20,180
♪ Every soul is bound by cause and fate ♪

91
00:08:18,000 --> 00:08:20,870
Xiao Wuyi!

92
00:08:20,450 --> 00:08:24,010
♪ The past is gone, so let it slip away ♪

93
00:08:22,870 --> 00:08:25,310
Mao, I'm so tired.

94
00:08:24,030 --> 00:08:27,000
♪ The heart's a cage,
but peace will break the chains ♪

95
00:08:25,800 --> 00:08:27,070
The Eagle King has treated me very well.

96
00:08:27,030 --> 00:08:32,500
♪ No need to speak,
just leave it all to fate ♪

97
00:08:27,720 --> 00:08:29,520
He knew all along that I was a spy,

98
00:08:29,560 --> 00:08:32,630
yet he still sincerely wanted to give me
a peaceful life for the years I had left.

99
00:08:32,630 --> 00:08:35,030
But I could never give him
my genuine affection.

100
00:08:35,030 --> 00:08:37,270
With the deep-seated hatred
between our Prince Qi's household and him,

101
00:08:37,270 --> 00:08:39,240
I could neither love him nor hate him.

102
00:08:39,240 --> 00:08:40,840
Once our two nations go to war,

103
00:08:40,840 --> 00:08:43,360
it's bound to be a fight
where one side must die.

104
00:08:43,360 --> 00:08:44,960
Today, I'm returning those 3 stolen years

105
00:08:44,960 --> 00:08:46,790
to Jiayu all at once.

106
00:08:47,480 --> 00:08:48,360
With my death,

107
00:08:48,790 --> 00:08:50,240
Xiao Wuyi should be able to gain

108
00:08:50,240 --> 00:08:51,630
the trust of Northern Qin.

109
00:08:51,630 --> 00:08:52,870
Perhaps this can finally atone

110
00:08:52,870 --> 00:08:55,000
for the sins I committed at Lingfeng Fort.

111
00:08:55,000 --> 00:08:56,910
Please allow me to use this life of mine

112
00:08:56,910 --> 00:08:58,550
to finally usher in the beginning of

113
00:08:58,550 --> 00:09:00,080
your imperial legacy, Mao.

114
00:09:01,000 --> 00:09:01,600
Mao.

115
00:09:02,030 --> 00:09:02,790
Forgive me.

116
00:09:03,360 --> 00:09:04,440
I want to rest now.

117
00:09:06,630 --> 00:09:07,440
Retreat!

118
00:09:20,790 --> 00:09:23,480
What if I don't want
to be the wife of the infamous Demon Xiao,

119
00:09:23,480 --> 00:09:24,840
but the wife of a hero?

120
00:09:25,800 --> 00:09:28,580
I want you to live a long life,

121
00:09:28,880 --> 00:09:29,920
to live in peace,

122
00:09:30,750 --> 00:09:32,630
to leave behind an honorable name,

123
00:09:32,630 --> 00:09:34,160
and to be remembered by all.

124
00:09:35,000 --> 00:09:36,670
You are making things difficult for me.

125
00:09:36,670 --> 00:09:37,470
That's right.

126
00:09:37,910 --> 00:09:39,040
I insist on doing so.

127
00:09:39,720 --> 00:09:40,920
Will you listen to me?

128
00:10:05,470 --> 00:10:08,890
♪ A dying memory glimmers low ♪

129
00:10:09,200 --> 00:10:12,810
♪ You appear, but I can't hold you so ♪

130
00:10:12,870 --> 00:10:13,790
On the day of the competition,

131
00:10:12,980 --> 00:10:17,340
♪ Time itself comes to a sudden halt ♪

132
00:10:13,910 --> 00:10:15,110
I took a liking to you.

133
00:10:16,200 --> 00:10:17,700
My desire to marry you
comes from my heart.

134
00:10:17,700 --> 00:10:20,400
♪ So desolate ♪

135
00:10:18,390 --> 00:10:19,450
It was never an act.

136
00:10:20,360 --> 00:10:21,080
It's no coincidence.

137
00:10:20,980 --> 00:10:24,650
♪ I traded obsession for this loss ♪

138
00:10:22,360 --> 00:10:24,420
I came here specifically to find you.

139
00:10:24,670 --> 00:10:28,210
♪ If I could lay my heart bare and cross ♪

140
00:10:25,000 --> 00:10:26,760
With such a beauty
throwing herself into my arms,

141
00:10:26,760 --> 00:10:28,360
how could I possibly refuse?

142
00:10:28,400 --> 00:10:33,730
♪ Would you once more have pity on me ♪

143
00:10:34,230 --> 00:10:37,050
♪ I fear no doom of endless karmic pain ♪

144
00:10:37,080 --> 00:10:39,570
♪ Only that you drift far from my side ♪

145
00:10:39,830 --> 00:10:44,000
♪ Apart from you,
the world is an endless night ♪

146
00:10:44,020 --> 00:10:47,620
♪ Even if my beating heart
wears thin and fades ♪

147
00:10:47,870 --> 00:10:49,640
♪ I'd choose this fate
till death's final line ♪

148
00:10:49,870 --> 00:10:52,490
♪ I only hope the mortal lands ♪

149
00:10:52,520 --> 00:10:55,180
♪ Can grant our wishes ♪

150
00:10:55,360 --> 00:10:59,600
♪ Through endless night,
let heaven and earth fall apart ♪

151
00:10:59,630 --> 00:11:04,470
♪ I just want to see you one more time ♪

152
00:11:12,200 --> 00:11:13,800
I've brought your two guards

153
00:11:13,910 --> 00:11:14,870
back to you.

154
00:11:16,630 --> 00:11:18,270
Aren't you worried I'll run away?

155
00:11:18,270 --> 00:11:19,000
Yesterday,

156
00:11:19,480 --> 00:11:20,940
in front of the two armies,

157
00:11:21,150 --> 00:11:23,410
you killed Li Lejun in front of everyone,

158
00:11:23,440 --> 00:11:25,100
proving your determination.

159
00:11:25,840 --> 00:11:27,440
With this pledge of loyalty,

160
00:11:27,630 --> 00:11:29,830
what more could I possibly worry about?

161
00:11:31,910 --> 00:11:32,550
What?

162
00:11:34,270 --> 00:11:35,330
You want to kill me?

163
00:11:37,240 --> 00:11:38,030
Xiao Wuyi.

164
00:11:38,250 --> 00:11:40,510
You've actually chosen to side with
the Northern Qin bandits.

165
00:11:40,510 --> 00:11:42,110
Are you still worthy of the title of
Crown Prince Wenxi?

166
00:11:42,110 --> 00:11:43,550
How can you face the brothers
of the Beifu Army?

167
00:11:43,550 --> 00:11:45,750
I, Xiao Wuyi, have never feared
what others say.

168
00:11:45,750 --> 00:11:46,840
If I hadn't done this,

169
00:11:46,840 --> 00:11:47,510
would you

170
00:11:47,680 --> 00:11:49,410
and those people of Southern Ye
trapped in that sheep pen

171
00:11:49,410 --> 00:11:51,140
still have a chance to survive?

172
00:11:51,630 --> 00:11:53,630
Li Mao slaughtered my entire family

173
00:11:53,720 --> 00:11:55,790
and seized control of the Beifu Army
from me.

174
00:11:55,790 --> 00:11:57,670
Now, driven by greed for glory,
he's rushing headlong into danger,

175
00:11:57,670 --> 00:11:59,530
poised to send our Beifu soldiers

176
00:11:59,630 --> 00:12:01,750
straight under the blades and axes
of the Northern Qin Army.

177
00:12:01,750 --> 00:12:03,790
When that happens, forget about
the Northern Expedition—

178
00:12:03,790 --> 00:12:06,030
even the entire Northern Border will fall.

179
00:12:06,030 --> 00:12:07,630
Soon enough, you'll find out

180
00:12:07,870 --> 00:12:10,320
who's right and who's wrong.

181
00:12:11,510 --> 00:12:12,970
My deal with the Eagle King

182
00:12:13,840 --> 00:12:14,790
is nothing more than a way to reclaim

183
00:12:14,790 --> 00:12:16,590
what originally belonged to me.

184
00:12:19,000 --> 00:12:21,630
Whether to stay... Or to leave,

185
00:12:23,150 --> 00:12:24,420
it's up to you.

186
00:12:26,600 --> 00:12:29,390
My parents were both killed
by the people of Northern Qin.

187
00:12:29,390 --> 00:12:31,840
I swear I'll never ally myself with
these bandits in this lifetime.

188
00:12:31,840 --> 00:12:32,670
Xiao Wuyi,

189
00:12:33,960 --> 00:12:36,890
you're not worthy of the title
of Crown Prince Wenxi.

190
00:12:41,480 --> 00:12:43,410
Please forgive us, Your Highness.

191
00:12:52,240 --> 00:12:53,640
Whether they live or die,

192
00:12:54,270 --> 00:12:56,440
Young Lord Xiao, it's your call.

193
00:12:56,840 --> 00:12:58,550
They're just 2 stray dogs.

194
00:12:59,510 --> 00:13:00,840
Let them get lost.

195
00:13:07,320 --> 00:13:08,250
Don't look back.

196
00:13:08,630 --> 00:13:10,560
The more isolated His Highness is,

197
00:13:10,600 --> 00:13:12,730
the more the Eagle King will trust him.

198
00:13:29,120 --> 00:13:30,980
Lejun wanted to completely sever

199
00:13:31,270 --> 00:13:33,200
the bond between you and Xiao Wuyi.

200
00:13:36,200 --> 00:13:37,800
Just like how it was back then

201
00:13:38,120 --> 00:13:39,450
with my mother's death.

202
00:13:41,440 --> 00:13:43,700
No matter how many reasons I came up with,

203
00:13:44,270 --> 00:13:45,320
or how many excuses I made for Lejun

204
00:13:45,320 --> 00:13:46,390
in my heart,

205
00:13:46,960 --> 00:13:48,420
the friendship between us

206
00:13:49,540 --> 00:13:51,070
still came to an abrupt end.

207
00:13:55,150 --> 00:13:56,030
Because

208
00:13:58,270 --> 00:13:59,800
that was my dearest mother.

209
00:14:01,360 --> 00:14:02,030
She always hoped

210
00:14:02,030 --> 00:14:03,690
I could become a true emperor,

211
00:14:06,120 --> 00:14:07,980
free from anyone's constraints.

212
00:14:10,150 --> 00:14:13,150
She was worried I'd become too dependent
on Xiao Wuyi,

213
00:14:14,240 --> 00:14:15,290
and that

214
00:14:18,720 --> 00:14:20,720
I'd let my guard down because of you.

215
00:14:24,200 --> 00:14:25,800
Through this deadly gambit,

216
00:14:26,910 --> 00:14:29,440
she fulfilled the plan
Wuyi and I had devised,

217
00:14:31,200 --> 00:14:32,390
yet she also severed all ties

218
00:14:32,390 --> 00:14:33,920
between us once and for all.

219
00:14:46,840 --> 00:14:49,440
"Five days from now,
when the north wind rises,

220
00:14:50,030 --> 00:14:51,430
meet at Dingfeng Slope."

221
00:14:52,000 --> 00:14:54,460
This was found on the sole of
Li Lejun's shoe.

222
00:15:07,240 --> 00:15:09,440
It seems the day for the decisive battle

223
00:15:10,870 --> 00:15:11,870
has finally come.

224
00:15:12,180 --> 00:15:14,110
The new caltrop fireball is ready.

225
00:15:14,510 --> 00:15:16,750
It's completely different from
the previous version.

226
00:15:16,750 --> 00:15:18,010
I'll take you to see it.

227
00:15:50,560 --> 00:15:51,270
I'll go make the record.

228
00:15:51,270 --> 00:15:51,820
Okay.

229
00:15:57,550 --> 00:15:58,720
This is called "stone fat,"

230
00:15:58,720 --> 00:16:00,000
also known as "weishui."

231
00:16:00,000 --> 00:16:02,320
Stone fat oil deposits
are different from lard or tallow.

232
00:16:02,320 --> 00:16:04,030
They form alongside mineral deposits.

233
00:16:04,030 --> 00:16:05,890
They are flammable but inedible,

234
00:16:06,080 --> 00:16:07,670
and even water cannot extinguish them.

235
00:16:07,670 --> 00:16:08,870
They can stretch for thousands of miles

236
00:16:08,870 --> 00:16:10,070
and burn without end.

237
00:16:12,550 --> 00:16:14,480
Even water can't extinguish them?

238
00:16:14,840 --> 00:16:15,790
Then with this substance,

239
00:16:15,790 --> 00:16:17,390
we'll surely be invincible.

240
00:16:22,000 --> 00:16:23,240
I once promised Wuyi

241
00:16:23,630 --> 00:16:27,150
that I'd create the caltrop fireball
before the Northern Expedition.

242
00:16:27,150 --> 00:16:29,630
Though he's not here today
and cannot see it,

243
00:16:30,870 --> 00:16:32,600
I haven't failed in my mission.

244
00:16:37,790 --> 00:16:38,650
I have to go now.

245
00:16:40,870 --> 00:16:41,800
But don't worry.

246
00:16:42,550 --> 00:16:46,280
Cui Shao'an is overseeing
the production of the caltrop fireball.

247
00:16:46,790 --> 00:16:48,250
Are you going to find Wuyi?

248
00:16:52,120 --> 00:16:53,640
This battle could result in
a great victory

249
00:16:53,640 --> 00:16:55,470
for the Beifu Army,

250
00:16:56,390 --> 00:16:57,670
for Ye, and for you.

251
00:16:58,550 --> 00:16:59,960
But for Xiao Wuyi,

252
00:17:01,310 --> 00:17:02,430
defeat is certain.

253
00:17:05,030 --> 00:17:06,910
He had already resolved to die,

254
00:17:07,589 --> 00:17:09,920
and now, the two-month deadline
is nearly up,

255
00:17:09,920 --> 00:17:12,200
and the miraculous doctor's medicine
won't last much longer.

256
00:17:12,200 --> 00:17:13,260
I won't let him die.

257
00:17:13,920 --> 00:17:15,119
I'm going to find him.

258
00:17:15,720 --> 00:17:17,849
I'll definitely bring him back alive.

259
00:17:19,550 --> 00:17:22,270
The loyalty to stand through
life and death together—

260
00:17:22,270 --> 00:17:23,800
that's the Xie Jiayu I know.

261
00:17:25,880 --> 00:17:26,400
Go on.

262
00:17:27,680 --> 00:17:28,790
You're not stopping me?

263
00:17:28,790 --> 00:17:29,440
I tried.

264
00:17:31,720 --> 00:17:32,580
But I couldn't.

265
00:17:35,590 --> 00:17:36,190
Take care.

266
00:17:37,330 --> 00:17:38,330
You take care too.

267
00:17:46,440 --> 00:17:49,040
Do you really have to go to
the Northern Border?

268
00:17:49,680 --> 00:17:51,680
I built the Beifu Army all by myself,

269
00:17:52,310 --> 00:17:54,640
and they once answered only to my command.

270
00:17:55,030 --> 00:17:59,000
Three years have passed since the reforms.
The military system may have changed,

271
00:17:59,000 --> 00:18:01,030
but the loyalty of the soldiers has not.

272
00:18:01,030 --> 00:18:01,680
Yizhi.

273
00:18:02,510 --> 00:18:05,640
The tragedy of the An and Lu families
must never happen again.

274
00:18:05,640 --> 00:18:07,070
The army's loyalty should not
lie with one man,

275
00:18:07,070 --> 00:18:08,200
but with the people.

276
00:18:09,480 --> 00:18:10,640
No matter who becomes the commander of

277
00:18:10,640 --> 00:18:11,500
the Beifu Army,

278
00:18:11,880 --> 00:18:13,510
and even without me, Xiao Wuyi,

279
00:18:13,510 --> 00:18:14,840
the Beifu Army must know

280
00:18:15,590 --> 00:18:17,250
that they are fighting for Ye.

281
00:18:17,920 --> 00:18:19,580
So you don't plan to come back?

282
00:18:23,310 --> 00:18:25,170
Will we ever see each other again?

283
00:18:38,110 --> 00:18:40,310
I hope that, in the final days of my life,

284
00:18:40,350 --> 00:18:42,950
I can pave the way for
the Northern Expedition.

285
00:18:44,590 --> 00:18:46,990
Was this your plan
from the very beginning?

286
00:18:48,440 --> 00:18:49,900
What about Xie Jiayu then?

287
00:18:51,680 --> 00:18:52,810
Tell Xiao Wuyi that,

288
00:18:53,550 --> 00:18:54,350
as he wished,

289
00:18:55,590 --> 00:18:58,650
the next time we meet,
it will be as emperor and subject.

290
00:19:01,240 --> 00:19:02,480
Got it, Mao.

291
00:19:03,510 --> 00:19:05,350
Goodbye, Yaoyao.

292
00:19:12,480 --> 00:19:13,880
Your Highness Prince Qi,

293
00:19:15,110 --> 00:19:16,370
I hereby take my leave.

294
00:19:27,240 --> 00:19:27,960
Goodbye,

295
00:19:30,110 --> 00:19:30,790
Xie Jiayu.

296
00:19:32,230 --> 00:19:35,650
♪ A dying memory glimmers low ♪

297
00:19:35,960 --> 00:19:39,630
♪ You appear, but I can't hold you so ♪

298
00:19:39,740 --> 00:19:44,110
♪ Time itself comes to a sudden halt ♪

299
00:19:40,580 --> 00:19:43,440
Bring all the military reports
and memorials here.

300
00:19:44,470 --> 00:19:47,160
♪ So desolate ♪

301
00:19:47,740 --> 00:19:51,410
♪ I traded obsession for this loss ♪

302
00:19:51,430 --> 00:19:54,970
♪ If I could lay my heart bare and cross ♪

303
00:19:55,160 --> 00:20:00,440
♪ Would you once more have pity on me ♪

304
00:20:00,480 --> 00:20:01,550
I won't get married.

305
00:20:01,140 --> 00:20:04,580
♪ If the heavens should change
and fate tear me apart ♪

306
00:20:02,420 --> 00:20:04,420
I just want to stay by your side, Mao.

307
00:20:04,600 --> 00:20:08,600
♪ Yet still cannot undo one beat
of my heart's art ♪

308
00:20:05,920 --> 00:20:08,650
I have the best older brother
in the entire world.

309
00:20:08,730 --> 00:20:12,440
♪ I've traveled so far—
the day I find you again ♪

310
00:20:10,720 --> 00:20:11,350
Mao.

311
00:20:12,470 --> 00:20:15,760
♪ I fear you might have forgotten me ♪

312
00:20:13,160 --> 00:20:15,090
I will protect you, no matter what.

313
00:20:16,080 --> 00:20:18,900
♪ I fear no doom of endless karmic pain ♪

314
00:20:18,930 --> 00:20:21,420
♪ Only that you drift far from my side ♪

315
00:20:22,060 --> 00:20:26,300
♪ Through endless night,
let heaven and earth fall apart ♪

316
00:20:26,630 --> 00:20:30,800
♪ I'd bid farewell to every worldly part ♪

317
00:20:30,990 --> 00:20:34,970
♪ Just to gaze upon you one last time ♪

318
00:20:43,110 --> 00:20:45,170
We've just received a battle report.

319
00:20:46,750 --> 00:20:49,030
Last night, scouts detected a sudden fire

320
00:20:49,030 --> 00:20:51,030
breaking out at the Beifu Army Camp.

321
00:20:51,240 --> 00:20:53,300
Li Mao's army immediately broke camp

322
00:20:53,680 --> 00:20:55,750
and marched westward,
bypassing the Jing River.

323
00:20:55,750 --> 00:20:57,410
He's going to Dingfeng Slope.

324
00:20:58,480 --> 00:20:59,410
Dingfeng Slope?

325
00:21:00,110 --> 00:21:01,710
Li Mao must be heading there,

326
00:21:01,920 --> 00:21:06,030
because Dingfeng Slope holds a secret
that has never been revealed to outsiders.

327
00:21:06,030 --> 00:21:06,920
What secret?

328
00:21:08,070 --> 00:21:09,560
To the south of Dingfeng Slope

329
00:21:09,560 --> 00:21:11,830
are 2 iron mines marked by
the Phoenix Heart Tokens.

330
00:21:11,830 --> 00:21:13,290
If he holds Dingfeng Slope

331
00:21:13,720 --> 00:21:16,030
and establishes
a Directorate of Military Equipment there,

332
00:21:16,030 --> 00:21:17,030
using it as a base

333
00:21:17,720 --> 00:21:18,960
to train troops, forge weapons,

334
00:21:18,960 --> 00:21:20,480
store grain, and raise livestock,

335
00:21:20,480 --> 00:21:22,400
not only will the capture of the Capital
be just a matter of time,

336
00:21:22,400 --> 00:21:25,830
but he'll also no longer have to rely on
the aristocratic clans for supplies.

337
00:21:25,830 --> 00:21:26,690
Your Highness.

338
00:21:27,920 --> 00:21:29,250
There's a woman outside

339
00:21:29,480 --> 00:21:31,480
claiming to be Xiao Wuyi's consort.

340
00:21:37,200 --> 00:21:38,440
Let me go.

341
00:21:40,350 --> 00:21:41,590
I just told you,

342
00:21:41,590 --> 00:21:42,990
I am Xiao Wuyi's consort.

343
00:21:43,680 --> 00:21:44,640
If you don't believe me,

344
00:21:44,640 --> 00:21:46,770
just call him out and ask him yourself.

345
00:21:47,110 --> 00:21:48,240
Xiao Wuyi, I'm here!

346
00:21:48,590 --> 00:21:49,320
Xiao Wuyi...

347
00:21:49,680 --> 00:21:50,350
Look at him.

348
00:21:50,440 --> 00:21:51,350
Just let me go.

349
00:21:52,110 --> 00:21:53,640
You... Tell him to let me go.

350
00:21:54,590 --> 00:21:55,190
Xiao Wuyi.

351
00:21:55,550 --> 00:21:56,680
What are you doing here?

352
00:21:56,680 --> 00:21:58,440
I'm here to share life and death with you.

353
00:21:58,440 --> 00:21:59,040
Xiao Wuyi.

354
00:21:59,510 --> 00:22:00,920
I had to set the Beifu Army Camp

355
00:22:00,920 --> 00:22:02,400
on fire just to escape.

356
00:22:02,790 --> 00:22:04,070
And this is how you greet me?

357
00:22:04,070 --> 00:22:07,270
All those days I spent crying for you
were for nothing then.

358
00:22:07,270 --> 00:22:09,640
Xie Jiayu, long time no see.

359
00:22:10,310 --> 00:22:11,240
It seems you are truly devoted

360
00:22:11,240 --> 00:22:12,680
to Young Lord Xiao.

361
00:22:15,440 --> 00:22:16,270
Let her in.

362
00:22:19,510 --> 00:22:20,070
Yes!

363
00:22:25,480 --> 00:22:27,280
The food is ready. Please enjoy.

364
00:22:37,590 --> 00:22:38,320
Xiao Wuyi...

365
00:22:56,270 --> 00:22:58,600
Now that you've escaped Li Mao's control,

366
00:22:58,830 --> 00:23:00,400
you could go anywhere you wish.

367
00:23:00,400 --> 00:23:02,400
Why come running here
and throw yourself into danger?

368
00:23:02,400 --> 00:23:03,270
Are you crazy?

369
00:23:09,030 --> 00:23:09,830
Don't you know

370
00:23:10,110 --> 00:23:11,480
that once you enter this place,

371
00:23:11,480 --> 00:23:13,480
leaving will be nearly impossible?

372
00:23:14,270 --> 00:23:16,200
How many times do I have to tell you?

373
00:23:17,070 --> 00:23:19,330
I'm here to share life and death
with you.

374
00:23:20,270 --> 00:23:21,000
Understood?

375
00:23:25,480 --> 00:23:26,160
But

376
00:23:26,720 --> 00:23:29,200
if you're bothered by the fact
that Li Mao forced me to marry him,

377
00:23:29,200 --> 00:23:30,660
then I'll leave right now.

378
00:23:31,440 --> 00:23:33,500
What nonsense are you talking about?

379
00:23:34,480 --> 00:23:36,880
Then why haven't you smiled at me
even once?

380
00:23:40,960 --> 00:23:42,620
I've already resolved to die.

381
00:23:45,550 --> 00:23:47,680
My reputation out there is in tatters.

382
00:23:47,720 --> 00:23:49,120
Why should I drag you down

383
00:23:49,480 --> 00:23:50,810
to suffer alongside me?

384
00:23:51,000 --> 00:23:53,330
Didn't we promise each other long ago that

385
00:23:53,880 --> 00:23:55,810
whether you achieve glory and fame

386
00:23:56,270 --> 00:23:57,870
or are reviled by the masses,

387
00:23:58,350 --> 00:23:59,950
I will always be by your side?

388
00:24:00,790 --> 00:24:02,450
I, Xie Jiayu, stand by my word.

389
00:24:05,270 --> 00:24:06,070
Xiao Wuyi.

390
00:24:07,270 --> 00:24:10,070
As husband and wife,
our fates are bound together.

391
00:24:10,350 --> 00:24:11,880
All I want is for you to live.

392
00:24:21,240 --> 00:24:22,900
Even if everyone abandons me,

393
00:24:23,830 --> 00:24:25,360
as long as you're by my side,

394
00:24:26,350 --> 00:24:29,010
I, Xiao Wuyi, won't have lived this life
in vain.

395
00:24:30,270 --> 00:24:32,130
Once I've wiped out Li Mao's army,

396
00:24:33,920 --> 00:24:34,980
I'll come find you.

397
00:24:37,750 --> 00:24:39,400
The weapon I promised you—

398
00:24:40,070 --> 00:24:41,600
I've successfully made it.

399
00:24:55,750 --> 00:24:56,610
Your Highness.

400
00:24:57,640 --> 00:24:58,960
Xiao Wuyi and Xie Jiayu

401
00:24:59,030 --> 00:25:00,560
have been doing nothing but

402
00:25:00,640 --> 00:25:01,960
eating and drinking all day.

403
00:25:01,960 --> 00:25:03,400
What do you make of this, Imperial Envoy

404
00:25:03,400 --> 00:25:04,860
Do you think Young Lord Xiao's consort

405
00:25:04,860 --> 00:25:06,420
really just came here

406
00:25:06,920 --> 00:25:08,620
to share life and death with Xiao Wuyi?

407
00:25:08,620 --> 00:25:10,750
I've heard a saying among common folk,

408
00:25:10,920 --> 00:25:12,920
"Husband and wife are like
birds of a feather.

409
00:25:12,920 --> 00:25:15,110
But when disaster strikes,
they fly their separate ways."

410
00:25:15,110 --> 00:25:16,750
Your Highness surely
doesn't really believe

411
00:25:16,750 --> 00:25:19,750
there's anyone in this world
who'd die for love, do you?

412
00:25:19,750 --> 00:25:21,410
I certainly don't believe it.

413
00:25:21,830 --> 00:25:23,960
But that Xie Jiayu is truly different.

414
00:25:24,680 --> 00:25:25,720
Back in Jiankang,

415
00:25:26,000 --> 00:25:28,060
Xiao Wuyi was deeply in love with her,

416
00:25:28,200 --> 00:25:30,110
yet she was childhood sweethearts
with Li Mao.

417
00:25:30,110 --> 00:25:31,710
Between Xiao Wuyi and Li Mao,

418
00:25:32,550 --> 00:25:34,950
Li Lejun's death was merely
the last straw.

419
00:25:35,440 --> 00:25:37,680
The one who truly drove those two apart

420
00:25:38,270 --> 00:25:39,270
was Xie Jiayu.

421
00:25:39,640 --> 00:25:41,160
Since Xiao Wuyi and Xie Jiayu

422
00:25:41,160 --> 00:25:42,420
share such a deep bond,

423
00:25:42,920 --> 00:25:44,920
doesn't that mean we've got

424
00:25:44,920 --> 00:25:46,460
even more leverage against Xiao Wuyi now?

425
00:25:46,460 --> 00:25:47,660
His Majesty means...

426
00:25:50,920 --> 00:25:53,310
This is a rare opportunity.

427
00:25:55,590 --> 00:25:57,680
Very well. As His Majesty commands,

428
00:25:58,400 --> 00:26:00,270
even if the mines at Dingfeng Slope

429
00:26:00,270 --> 00:26:01,930
turn out to be a colossal trap,

430
00:26:02,310 --> 00:26:03,880
we shall still brave it.

431
00:26:04,310 --> 00:26:05,980
Beat the drums and muster the troops!

432
00:26:05,980 --> 00:26:06,710
Understood!

433
00:26:16,480 --> 00:26:18,940
Your Highness, please don't go
any further.

434
00:26:21,830 --> 00:26:22,540
Got it.

435
00:26:23,290 --> 00:26:24,620
You all head back first.

436
00:26:26,830 --> 00:26:27,350
What?

437
00:26:27,880 --> 00:26:29,880
Are Heir's words
no longer enough to command you?

438
00:26:29,880 --> 00:26:30,880
His Highness said

439
00:26:31,110 --> 00:26:32,790
that Heir's an important guest here,

440
00:26:32,790 --> 00:26:34,270
yet you keep watching us every day.

441
00:26:34,270 --> 00:26:37,470
Do you intend to eavesdrop
on our private affairs as well?

442
00:26:38,830 --> 00:26:39,440
Step back.

443
00:26:57,400 --> 00:26:58,310
The Eagle King probably thought

444
00:26:58,310 --> 00:27:00,030
you came here to gather information.

445
00:27:00,030 --> 00:27:01,290
Who would have thought

446
00:27:01,680 --> 00:27:03,610
you really came to join me in death?

447
00:27:04,310 --> 00:27:05,400
So, are you saying

448
00:27:05,400 --> 00:27:06,660
I shouldn't have come?

449
00:27:11,350 --> 00:27:12,410
I didn't mean that.

450
00:27:13,590 --> 00:27:14,590
Tell me the truth—

451
00:27:14,590 --> 00:27:16,350
were you happy to see me?

452
00:27:19,830 --> 00:27:20,350
I was.

453
00:27:22,830 --> 00:27:23,630
I was so happy.

454
00:27:25,920 --> 00:27:27,580
Then do you know how upset I was

455
00:27:27,590 --> 00:27:28,850
when I saw your letter?

456
00:27:31,750 --> 00:27:34,000
Xiao Wuyi, if you ever do
something like this again,

457
00:27:34,000 --> 00:27:35,900
I will absolutely not forgive you.

458
00:27:35,900 --> 00:27:36,620
Or

459
00:27:36,650 --> 00:27:38,380
you can just go live with Li Mao.

460
00:27:40,680 --> 00:27:42,960
No, that's not right either. Li Mao said

461
00:27:44,640 --> 00:27:45,840
the next time you met,

462
00:27:46,480 --> 00:27:47,350
as you wished,

463
00:27:47,640 --> 00:27:49,370
it'd be as emperor and subject.

464
00:27:52,440 --> 00:27:54,000
The coroner has done the autopsy.

465
00:27:54,000 --> 00:27:55,270
Before Lejun died,

466
00:27:55,270 --> 00:27:56,930
she had already taken poison.

467
00:27:57,540 --> 00:27:59,700
You never meant to shoot that arrow.

468
00:28:01,000 --> 00:28:02,800
Even if Li Lejun had taken poison

469
00:28:04,160 --> 00:28:05,490
and was destined to die,

470
00:28:06,960 --> 00:28:08,490
Lejun was still his sister.

471
00:28:09,830 --> 00:28:11,290
In the end, what that arrow

472
00:28:12,510 --> 00:28:14,030
shot through was the youthful friendship

473
00:28:14,030 --> 00:28:15,630
between Xiao Wuyi and Li Mao.

474
00:28:16,960 --> 00:28:18,360
Then on the battlefield,

475
00:28:19,270 --> 00:28:19,920
you two...

476
00:28:20,960 --> 00:28:22,110
No matter how my relationship with Yizhi

477
00:28:22,110 --> 00:28:23,030
changes,

478
00:28:24,270 --> 00:28:25,800
when it comes to Southern Ye

479
00:28:25,880 --> 00:28:27,480
and the affairs of the court,

480
00:28:27,590 --> 00:28:29,920
we'll always share the same aspirations.

481
00:28:31,750 --> 00:28:33,880
This is something he'll never change.

482
00:28:36,750 --> 00:28:39,010
Now that so many people have sacrificed,

483
00:28:39,550 --> 00:28:41,550
no matter how hard the road ahead is,

484
00:28:42,550 --> 00:28:44,950
we must persevere and keep moving forward.

485
00:28:45,790 --> 00:28:46,880
Did Lejun

486
00:28:48,200 --> 00:28:49,640
leave any final words?

487
00:28:55,590 --> 00:28:57,120
If you ever have the chance,

488
00:28:57,640 --> 00:29:00,100
please deliver this message to Jiayu
for me:

489
00:29:01,400 --> 00:29:02,860
I have never done anything

490
00:29:03,590 --> 00:29:05,110
in my life that I regret.

491
00:29:06,680 --> 00:29:08,210
Be it resentment or hatred,

492
00:29:08,920 --> 00:29:10,720
I've accepted it all willingly.

493
00:29:11,310 --> 00:29:13,040
As I reach the end of my journey,

494
00:29:13,350 --> 00:29:14,280
my only regret is

495
00:29:15,110 --> 00:29:16,790
that I won't be able to

496
00:29:18,400 --> 00:29:20,930
view the beautiful landscapes
of Ye with her.

497
00:29:24,790 --> 00:29:25,920
Why are you sighing?

498
00:29:28,590 --> 00:29:29,200
Nothing.

499
00:29:30,270 --> 00:29:32,400
I just hope when we return to Jiankang,

500
00:29:32,830 --> 00:29:35,960
we'll still make it in time for
the Thousand Lantern Festival.

501
00:29:35,960 --> 00:29:38,420
The journey of life is like
sailing on a boat.

502
00:29:39,950 --> 00:29:42,620
The passengers come and go,

503
00:29:44,110 --> 00:29:45,030
and some people

504
00:29:46,200 --> 00:29:48,720
are destined to accompany you
only for a part of the journey.

505
00:29:48,720 --> 00:29:51,480
When their time comes, they will leave.

506
00:29:54,790 --> 00:29:56,050
We must learn to let go.

507
00:29:57,240 --> 00:29:58,350
That may be true,

508
00:29:59,550 --> 00:30:00,240
but I don't want to hear

509
00:30:00,240 --> 00:30:01,440
any words of ill omen.

510
00:30:01,640 --> 00:30:02,400
Not today,

511
00:30:02,880 --> 00:30:03,720
not tomorrow.

512
00:30:06,070 --> 00:30:07,750
Xiao Wuyi, hold out your hand.

513
00:30:17,110 --> 00:30:17,840
What is this?

514
00:30:18,070 --> 00:30:19,530
This is a life-saving pill

515
00:30:19,750 --> 00:30:21,680
I begged the miraculous doctor to make.

516
00:30:21,680 --> 00:30:22,590
Keep it safe.

517
00:30:36,400 --> 00:30:38,000
Why are there so many people?

518
00:30:48,750 --> 00:30:49,610
Your Highness.

519
00:30:53,200 --> 00:30:54,440
What's this supposed to mean?

520
00:30:54,440 --> 00:30:55,640
Throughout history,

521
00:30:55,750 --> 00:30:56,960
whenever generals went off to war,

522
00:30:56,960 --> 00:30:59,070
their family members were often
held as hostages.

523
00:30:59,070 --> 00:31:01,640
Li Lejun took this poison as well.

524
00:31:04,480 --> 00:31:05,640
As long as we win,

525
00:31:06,240 --> 00:31:09,380
Young Lord Xiao, your consort
and the people of Southern Ye

526
00:31:09,380 --> 00:31:11,040
will surely be safe and sound.

527
00:31:30,920 --> 00:31:33,310
Your Highness, this place is surrounded by
mountains on all sides,

528
00:31:33,310 --> 00:31:35,600
with only a small road
leading out to the northeast.

529
00:31:35,600 --> 00:31:37,800
If the Beifu Army are to block this road,

530
00:31:37,960 --> 00:31:39,640
we'll be trapped here with no escape.

531
00:31:39,640 --> 00:31:41,440
Although this map is authentic,

532
00:31:41,790 --> 00:31:44,520
I fear Young Lord Xiao
may have ulterior motives.

533
00:31:46,400 --> 00:31:47,200
Pass my order:

534
00:31:47,790 --> 00:31:48,750
Act as usual.

535
00:31:49,270 --> 00:31:50,270
Lure the enemy in!

536
00:31:50,400 --> 00:31:51,060
Roger that!

537
00:31:52,960 --> 00:31:55,420
It seems Your Highness
has never trusted me.

538
00:31:56,110 --> 00:31:58,060
Was my acting really that bad?

539
00:31:58,550 --> 00:32:00,440
Your acting was excellent,
Young Lord Xiao.

540
00:32:00,440 --> 00:32:02,350
It's just a pity I don't care for plays.

541
00:32:02,350 --> 00:32:04,960
If you told me you were
plotting a rebellion, I'd believe it.

542
00:32:04,960 --> 00:32:06,720
But that you'd defect to Northern Qin?

543
00:32:06,720 --> 00:32:08,440
No matter how well your acting was,

544
00:32:08,440 --> 00:32:09,640
I'd never believe it.

545
00:32:14,750 --> 00:32:16,080
My men have all arrived.

546
00:32:16,550 --> 00:32:17,410
Today is the day

547
00:32:17,920 --> 00:32:19,390
that Beifu meets its end!

548
00:32:41,680 --> 00:32:42,830
They are all still alive?

549
00:32:42,830 --> 00:32:44,110
Even if the Xiao family were to die,

550
00:32:44,110 --> 00:32:46,110
they'd only die on the battlefield.

551
00:32:46,110 --> 00:32:48,110
How could they possibly die because of
your schemes and treachery?

552
00:32:48,110 --> 00:32:51,200
So it was all fake
from the very beginning?

553
00:32:52,030 --> 00:32:53,160
Warriors of Beifu!

554
00:32:54,590 --> 00:32:59,720
Charge!

555
00:32:59,720 --> 00:33:03,510
Kill!

556
00:33:10,640 --> 00:33:11,800
Wuyi, catch this!

557
00:33:19,880 --> 00:33:21,200
Move, move. Faster.

558
00:33:21,920 --> 00:33:22,630
Faster!

559
00:33:23,030 --> 00:33:23,440
Move.

560
00:33:24,400 --> 00:33:24,950
Hurry up!

561
00:33:25,680 --> 00:33:26,270
Hurry!

562
00:33:29,870 --> 00:33:30,600
Move faster!

563
00:33:31,030 --> 00:33:31,550
Come on!

564
00:33:33,830 --> 00:33:34,480
Faster!

565
00:33:34,750 --> 00:33:36,210
What are you dawdling for?

566
00:33:51,440 --> 00:33:52,110
Promise me

567
00:33:54,200 --> 00:33:56,060
you'll take good care of yourself

568
00:33:58,750 --> 00:34:00,280
and wait for me to come back.

569
00:34:01,110 --> 00:34:02,000
Xiao Wuyi.

570
00:34:02,200 --> 00:34:03,000
You liar!

571
00:34:03,550 --> 00:34:04,350
Move, move.

572
00:34:07,510 --> 00:34:08,230
Faster!

573
00:34:09,110 --> 00:34:10,000
Move faster!

574
00:34:12,070 --> 00:34:12,510
Move.

575
00:34:15,480 --> 00:34:16,070
Grandma!

576
00:34:16,120 --> 00:34:16,760
What are you doing?

577
00:34:16,760 --> 00:34:17,360
Hurry up.

578
00:34:18,070 --> 00:34:19,130
What are you doing?

579
00:34:19,880 --> 00:34:20,590
Stop hitting him!

580
00:34:20,590 --> 00:34:21,190
Get up!

581
00:34:29,360 --> 00:34:30,110
My kid...

582
00:34:30,110 --> 00:34:31,960
What are you looking at? Get to work!

583
00:34:31,960 --> 00:34:34,000
Killing is for the sake of saving lives.

584
00:34:34,000 --> 00:34:34,760
Xie Jiayu.

585
00:34:35,510 --> 00:34:37,170
You're not left with nothing.

586
00:34:48,810 --> 00:34:50,630
The Northern Qin people see us Ye people
as nothing more than pigs and sheep

587
00:34:50,630 --> 00:34:51,960
to be slaughtered.
Rather than waiting here to die

588
00:34:51,960 --> 00:34:53,000
and be slaughtered,

589
00:34:53,000 --> 00:34:54,530
why not take up your weapons

590
00:34:54,800 --> 00:34:55,659
and fight them?

591
00:34:58,880 --> 00:35:00,030
They are no different from us.

592
00:35:00,030 --> 00:35:01,230
They are also made of flesh and blood.

593
00:35:01,230 --> 00:35:02,960
They too will die and feel fear.

594
00:35:20,760 --> 00:35:21,440
Don't you

595
00:35:22,070 --> 00:35:24,630
want to go home?

596
00:35:27,270 --> 00:35:29,000
We all will die sooner or later.

597
00:35:29,000 --> 00:35:30,460
At worst, we die together!

598
00:35:31,920 --> 00:35:33,230
No one is born a coward.

599
00:35:33,920 --> 00:35:36,320
It's just when they become accustomed to
bowing their heads,

600
00:35:36,320 --> 00:35:37,850
courage and determination

601
00:35:38,110 --> 00:35:39,910
must be shown to them by someone—

602
00:35:39,960 --> 00:35:41,480
with their life and blood.

603
00:35:52,400 --> 00:35:53,600
You came just in time.

604
00:35:53,630 --> 00:35:54,550
Let's get this over with quickly

605
00:35:54,550 --> 00:35:55,510
and go save Xiao Wuyi.

606
00:35:55,510 --> 00:35:58,110
He's about to take the Eagle King
down with him.

607
00:36:29,250 --> 00:36:29,770
Father.

608
00:36:34,800 --> 00:36:36,550
Xiao Wuyi, you've lost.

609
00:36:38,000 --> 00:36:39,260
Today, Dingfeng Slope

610
00:36:39,710 --> 00:36:41,760
will be the graveyard
for both you and the Beifu Army!

611
00:36:41,760 --> 00:36:43,020
Who wins and who loses,

612
00:36:43,670 --> 00:36:45,030
who lives and who dies—

613
00:36:45,920 --> 00:36:47,450
it still remains to be seen.

614
00:36:55,590 --> 00:36:57,390
His Majesty's army has arrived!

615
00:37:14,400 --> 00:37:14,920
Defend!

616
00:37:29,250 --> 00:37:29,780
Retreat!

617
00:37:36,920 --> 00:37:37,550
Attack!

618
00:37:37,800 --> 00:37:38,440
Attack!

619
00:37:38,630 --> 00:37:39,510
Attack!

620
00:37:39,510 --> 00:37:41,360
Attack!

621
00:37:53,070 --> 00:37:53,760
Eagle King.

622
00:37:54,270 --> 00:37:55,530
How could you run away?

623
00:37:56,070 --> 00:37:57,760
This battle has just begun.

624
00:37:59,000 --> 00:38:00,480
So you threw yourself into this

625
00:38:00,480 --> 00:38:01,440
not for me,

626
00:38:01,920 --> 00:38:02,520
but for...

627
00:38:02,800 --> 00:38:05,440
Think about it. Prince Qi wouldn't let me
take all the military credit.

628
00:38:05,440 --> 00:38:06,280
Then would your young emperor

629
00:38:06,280 --> 00:38:08,280
spare a powerful minister like you?

630
00:38:08,920 --> 00:38:10,590
Now that we've both suffered heavy losses,

631
00:38:10,590 --> 00:38:12,120
he wants to reap the spoils.

632
00:38:12,360 --> 00:38:13,480
But little does he know

633
00:38:13,480 --> 00:38:15,480
that he's the real prey in this game.

634
00:38:45,110 --> 00:38:45,710
Load!

635
00:38:48,480 --> 00:38:49,110
Prime!

636
00:38:53,760 --> 00:38:54,480
Fire!

637
00:39:17,960 --> 00:39:21,000
So this is the true main force
of the Beifu Army.

638
00:39:21,320 --> 00:39:22,100
The Beifu Army

639
00:39:22,100 --> 00:39:24,550
has burned and cut off
all the escape routes from Dingfeng Slope!

640
00:39:24,550 --> 00:39:27,840
Xiao Wuyi saw that I was at odds with
His Majesty,

641
00:39:28,880 --> 00:39:30,150
so he deliberately put himself
into this fray,

642
00:39:30,150 --> 00:39:31,920
all to lure His Majesty into taking action
so he could wipe out the main force

643
00:39:31,920 --> 00:39:34,670
of our Northern Qin Army
here at Dingfeng Slope.

644
00:39:35,670 --> 00:39:36,760
He and his father

645
00:39:37,310 --> 00:39:39,110
never intended to return alive.

646
00:39:42,230 --> 00:39:43,550
Even if I die today,

647
00:39:44,320 --> 00:39:46,120
I'll personally finish you off!

648
00:39:58,590 --> 00:39:59,110
Yao!

649
00:40:41,670 --> 00:40:44,000
Father!

650
00:40:52,860 --> 00:40:53,510
Father...

651
00:41:05,760 --> 00:41:06,400
Father...

652
00:41:23,710 --> 00:41:26,280
Father!

653
00:41:44,390 --> 00:41:45,790
-Father!
-Yao, let's go!

654
00:41:46,440 --> 00:41:47,240
I won't leave.

655
00:42:04,840 --> 00:42:05,770
Don't look back.

656
00:42:06,010 --> 00:42:06,570
Go!

657
00:42:06,630 --> 00:42:07,280
Father!

658
00:42:17,190 --> 00:42:19,440
Wuyi, I can agree to your plan,

659
00:42:19,800 --> 00:42:21,310
but you need to agree to one condition:

660
00:42:21,310 --> 00:42:22,440
you must stay alive.

661
00:42:23,190 --> 00:42:24,630
Those with ambition cling to life;

662
00:42:24,630 --> 00:42:26,630
those who die for their cause seek death.

663
00:42:26,630 --> 00:42:28,960
Xiao Wuyi, cling to life for me
from now on,

664
00:42:29,670 --> 00:42:30,280
will you?

665
00:42:31,230 --> 00:42:32,510
I'm sorry, Yaoyao.

666
00:43:10,920 --> 00:43:11,670
Fire!

667
00:43:18,360 --> 00:43:18,960
Xiao Wuyi!

668
00:43:19,320 --> 00:43:20,050
You lunatic!

669
00:43:20,480 --> 00:43:21,710
As Crown Prince Wenxi,

670
00:43:21,710 --> 00:43:23,440
do you really have no regard
for your own life?

671
00:43:23,440 --> 00:43:24,370
Someone like you

672
00:43:25,030 --> 00:43:27,230
will never understand
what I've been fighting for in this life.
